snippet.title: Dead Pixels PC launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Dead Pixels is now available on PC and Xbox.
http://deadpixelsthegame.com

Get it for PC here: http://www.desura.com/games/dead-pixels
or on the Xbox here: http://marketplace.xbox.com/Product/Dead-Pixels/66acd000-77fe-1000-9115-d80258550970


Music by Daniel Bautista and KOU-G.

Voice over by:
Ed Khoo
Jonathan Cooke
Andrew "Noves" Miller
